Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安！ 里克~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安！ 妮莉絲每次都很早就來叫我了呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是指什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是你最勤奮的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼我就每天都來叫你起床吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不  不用這樣也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}家裡的平底鍋都要敲壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:11.61,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\bord1\fad(450,400)\blur6\pos(1070,178)}機械人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天看來不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為暴風雨的關係 海裡面也變得很吵雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}魚兒也都沒辦法法安靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爺爺 看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天就先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 身體不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從那邊讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了~ 在算便宜點吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行 不行 要殺價去找別家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼 真小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是剛烤好的麵包哦 請取用哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了 這是今天的外送麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈~ 好香的味道~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大海的情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天完全沒收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然魚量不多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是東面的海裡 好像有什麼在閃閃發光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦！？ 什麼什麼~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道是沉睡在海底的寶藏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算是的話 我也沒有興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別從大海裡拿走除了吃的以外的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這座島上自古流傳下來的訓誡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還真相信這種規定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我還有要送的麵包 那麼下次見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天美味的麵包 我期待著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說那個地方有著什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:12.75,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs62\bord1\fad(400,450)\blur6\pos(644,622)}— 診所 —
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}只要把里克的麵包放在屋子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}那孩子好像什麼時候就會吃掉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯哼哼~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能躲起來吃的話 會更好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是體力同時也在恢復的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天也醒的特別早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好香的味道啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是里克用心烤的麵包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定會好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}用心？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}隆醫生可以稍微餵她吃點東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確認 執行系統恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}執行救出作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等待自我再生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等待...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克的麵包對輝夜的健康有著很大的作用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說亞蜜露怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明不是最努力送麵包的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她有點其他事...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個可以稍微借我一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快從那裡讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你想做什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候里克的表情 第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}輝夜真是個神秘的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然恢復記憶的話 里克會...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}亞蜜露也在擔心這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在也只能相信他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.46,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs62\bord1\fad(450,0)\blur6\pos(644,622)}— 小梅古董店 —
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}就是這個發光的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暴風雨過後的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}燈火管制的那天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為寶石來說我覺得沒什麼珍貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個掛墜怎麼了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前不久漂流到海灘上的女孩拿著的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從哪裡來的 感覺能從這個掛墜裡找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直有人漂流到這個小島上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也是漂流過來的吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有以前的記憶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝了 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊... 等一下啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}實際上有件好消息想告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好消息？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大海裡面可能會有寶藏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「看到了海裡有閃閃發光的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}約翰也這麼說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為之前的暴風雨海底的形狀改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以前被埋沒的寶藏可能就因此出現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是海底的石頭在發光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前面調查過了 雖然是看以前的書的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像以前海盜船在東面的海裡觸礁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就把寶藏的一部分扔到海裡了呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小島的規定該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}除了吃的東西以外...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種事就不要在意了~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我聽說了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}麵包店的烤爐也需要修理費吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克也好像才來小島沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也沒必要在意古老的規定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不快點的話 寶藏可能被先拿走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊啊~ 約翰的話肯定會贊同我的~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們肯幫忙的話 我們就平分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是是37開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們這邊是7嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開什麼玩笑~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼先下水看看情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果能拿上來的話就拿上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能這麼順利嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起什麼都不做被別人搶掉的話要好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一個很大的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是一個人完全搬不動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在海裡直接把箱子砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看樣子就覺得很堅固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼只有用繩子固定住在拉上來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}變成麻煩的事情了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不是什麼事都還沒做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拉上來的勞力工作就交給你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還沒上來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧 妮莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手臂卡住的時候可能是沙石堆滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手臂左右晃動一下 應該就能簡單的就能抽出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃... 真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你才更適合下水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 萬一發生什麼事 先保存一下自己的體力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是一點都不肯吃虧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉~ 抱歉~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來~ 里克 該你發揮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}儘管用力拉上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一、二！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}用力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一、二！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}用力...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}痛痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再來一次吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒體力了~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可能用繩子拉上來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只能放棄了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是漢克工坊的煙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦對 就是那個啦！~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:38.96,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs62\bord3\fad(450,0)\blur8\pos(644,622)}— 漢克工坊 —
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}拜託了~ 請幫幫我們吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽說漢克的那個機器有很大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有在加上我這個嚴密的計劃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是嚴密的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該不需要我的幫助也能輕鬆的拉上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不快點的話 可能就被誰拿走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在東面的海裡看到閃閃發光的東西的情報已經散佈全鎮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯哼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}東面的海裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 很在意的吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瞧 就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}特別閃亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了呢？ 漢克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這下你又能動起來了呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}OK~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備好了唷~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}東西連動都沒動過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為有水壓 接下來才是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘛... 好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊 利用爆炸的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}水的流向變得混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試著改一下齒輪轉速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這艘船可是借來的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有小小的犧牲是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備怎麼辦 現在放開繩子也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}繼續下去吧 但是傷害要控制在最小哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}火藥石還剩一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要沒用錯時機的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克 把我胸前口袋裡的火藥石拿出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是現在啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我上了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}推倒它！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}欸咿...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咿...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唷喔喔喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}酷咿~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼樣阿~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的！~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是說過了 要把傷害控制在最小嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是這個~ 這個~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是罕見的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得應該是獨角獸的角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還沒加工的鉛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被大炮當做子彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才這麼重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒看見值得讓我們這麼辛苦的寶物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道發現真正的寶物了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是機械人偶尋找的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}糟糕 現在發光的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確認 執行系統還原事項
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}執行救出作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等待自我重生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等待...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果讓機械人偶啟動的話 這個小島會...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 那是什麼 讓我看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我看看嘛！~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拿的東西全部放在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海裡面拉上來的東西全部由王國來管理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直被盯著的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得到沉睡在海裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並不是好事只是無謂的爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們這幾個也應該知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有異議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}漢克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 至少留下當做修理費的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有異議的話 去城堡裡說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們只是回收從海裡打撈的東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這也是小島的規定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別從大海裡拿走除了吃的以外的東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這算什麼啊！ 為什麼全都要給王國呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}傍晚 有罕見的客人來買甜麵包了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像有什麼不可告人原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}妮莉絲~ 艾雅莉~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要稍微調查一下嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur5}下回 也為了做出幸福的麵包~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:40.06,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8\fs60\pos(640,424)}次章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:40.06,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\blur8\pos(640,512)}就像融化一般
